*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Modulpool Z001
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
PROGRAM Z001.

DATA: OKCODE100 TYPE SY-UCOMM,
      LV_ATTEMPTS TYPE I.

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Module BEFORE_LOGIN OUTPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE BEFORE_LOGIN OUTPUT.
* SET PF-STATUS 'xxxxxxxx'.
* SET TITLEBAR 'xxx'.

 DATA: IN_LOGIN100     TYPE C LENGTH 20,
       IN_PASSWORD100  TYPE C LENGTH 20.

ENDMODULE.


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Module  AFTER_LOGIN  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE AFTER_LOGIN INPUT.

CALL FUNCTION 'ZLOGIN001'
  EXPORTING
    IN_LOGIN100          = IN_LOGIN100
    IN_PASSWORD100       = IN_PASSWORD100
    OKCODE100            = OKCODE100
          .

ENDMODULE.
